---
const SITE_NAME = "The-Circle";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Fantasy • {SITE_NAME}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="The-Circle Fantasy: a league-focused hub for rules, standings, trash talk, and tools." />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="top">
      <div class="container nav">
        <a class="brand" href="/"><span class="mark"></span><span>{SITE_NAME}</span></a>
        <nav class="links">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/discord">Discord</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
          <a class="pill" href="/join">Join</a>
        </nav>
        <a class="pill mobileJoin" href="/join">Join</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
      <section class="card">
        <h1>The-Circle League</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          The goal is a clean home base for leagues: rules, season info, standings, and a place for trash talk that isn’t a cluttered mess.
        </p>

        <div class="grid">
          <div class="tile">
            <h2>League hub</h2>
            <p>One place for rules, schedules, payouts, and season notes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tile">
            <h2>Trash talk board</h2>
            <p>Keep it fun, keep it readable, and keep it in one spot.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tile">
            <h2>Tools (coming)</h2>
            <p>Draft helpers, keeper notes, rivalries, weekly summaries.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tile">
            <h2>Not Yahoo 2.0</h2>
            <p>We’re not trying to rebuild the whole platform. We’re building a better home for your league.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="fine">
          This page is the “product landing.” When you’re ready, we can add a real league portal behind login.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <style>
      :global(body){margin:0;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);
      background:radial-gradient(900px 500px at 15% 10%, rgba(9,255,3,.14), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(800px 450px at 85% 15%, rgba(120,170,255,.18), transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(700px 450px at 55% 95%, rgba(255,170,120,.10), transparent 55%), #070a0f;}
      a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
      .container{max-width:1020px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 18px}
      .top{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);background:rgba(7,10,15,.55);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10)}
      .nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 18px;gap:14px}
      .brand{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.02em;white-space:nowrap}
      .mark{width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:999px;background:#09ff03;box-shadow:0 0 0 6px rgba(9,255,3,.12), 0 0 28px rgba(9,255,3,.25)}
      .links{display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:center}
      .links a{color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);font-size:14px}
      .links a:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.95)}
      .pill{padding:10px 12px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid rgba(9,255,3,.24);background:rgba(9,255,3,.10);color:rgba(255,255,255,.95)!important}
      .mobileJoin{display:none}
      .card{margin:28px 0;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-radius:18px;padding:20px;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.45)}
      h1{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-0.02em}
      h2{margin:0 0 6px;font-size:18px}
      .lead{color:rgba(255,255,255,.72);font-size:17px;line-height:1.6;max-width:78ch}
      .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:12px;margin-top:14px}
      .tile{border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:16px;padding:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
      .tile p{margin:0;color:rgba(255,255,255,.72);line-height:1.55}
      .fine{margin-top:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);font-size:13px}
      @media (max-width:820px){.links{display:none}.mobileJoin{display:inline-flex}.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
